estions related to the Islamic text have been discussed in recent scholarship.  aIssued also in print.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 28. Mrz 2023) 7aRELIGION / Islam / Koran & Sacred Writings.2bisacsh  aIslam.  aQur'an.  aTextual criticism.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertDG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1z97831111757820 cEPUBz97831107714420 cprintz978311077087240uhttps://doi.org/10.1515/978311077132940uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9783110771329423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9783110771329/original  a978-3-11-117578-2  DG Plus DeG Package 2023 Part 1b2023  aEBA_CL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_DGALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_PLTLJSIS  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK